Bayan da Wilombey mai shekara 37 ta wallafa a shafinta na Instagram cewa tana shirin barin Truly, Jones ya tashi daga Birtaniya zuwa wasu gidajensa na rani.
Wani rahoto ya ce: "True ba ta cikin abubuwan da Holly Willows ke fifitawa.
