Guguwar da ake kira Hurricane Rosa ta kai gudun mil 85 a matsayin guguwa mai lamba 1 a safiyar yau Lahadi da safiya a daidai lokacin da ake amfani da saura mil 385 a kudu maso yammacin Punda Euhenia, Mexico.
