Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da aka ba da a ranar Alhamis, a kan wanda ya ke neman a naɗa shi a matsayin babban alƙali a kotun kolin Amurka, wato Brett Kavanaugh, da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin mata a shekarun 1980, Christine Blazey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin guda shida.
A halin yanzu, an ci gaba da samun rikice-rikice a fagen siyasa, inda gidajen talabijin suka katse shirin da aka saba gudanarwa a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi da FBI don gudanar da bincike na mako guda a kan zargin.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa a wani biki da suka yi a makarantar sakandare, Kavanaugh ya yi mata bara yayin da yake cikin maye kuma ya yi kokarin cire mata rigar.
Kavanaugh, a wata shaidar da aka shigar a kotu, ya ce yana da tabbacin cewa babu abin da ya faru.
Bisa ga kididdigar da kamfanin Nielsen ya yi, wataƙila fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan taron a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya lissafa matsakaicin kallon talabijin a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da kuma MSNBC.
Ba a samu adadin mutanen nan ba a sauran gidajen rediyo da suka nuna wannan sauraron, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da kuma Fox Business Network.
Duk da yake, Nielsen yawanci yana da wahala a ƙididdige yawan masu kallo da ke kallon watsa shirye-shirye daga ofisoshin ofisoshin.
Bari mu duba wannan kallon a girmansa, wannan masu sauraro ne masu girman kallon wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma na Oscar.
Fox News, wanda 'yan jarida suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ya sami matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a duk tsawon sauraron, a cewar Nielsen.
A matsayi na biyu, ABC tana da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ya biyo baya da miliyan 3.1, NBC da miliyan 2.94, MSNBC da miliyan 2.89 da CNN da miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
