Jerrard ya ci gaba da zama a ragar farko ba tare da nasara ba a gasar zakarun Turai a bana, inda za su kara da Hart, wanda ke da tazarar maki takwas, a ranar Lahadi mai zuwa.
Kafin wannan wasan, Rangers za ta karbi bakuncin Rapid Vienna a gasar Europa a ranar Alhamis.
A halin yanzu, Livingston ba ta yi nasara ba a wasanni shida a gasar, kuma koci Holt bai yi rashin nasara ba tun lokacin da ya maye gurbin Kenny Miller a watan da ya gabata.
Livingston ta yi hasarar damar da take da ita a gaban baƙi.
Holt ya kamata ya yi nasara kafin ya ci kwallo, kuma hakan ya sa Ranger a cikin matsala.
Scott Robinson ya ci gaba kuma ya kusan kai ga ƙarshe, amma Alan Lithgow ya hana shi yin hakan ta hanyar jefa kan Craig Halkett a kan hanya.
Masu filin wasa sun yarda Rangers su buga wasan a gabansu, domin sun san cewa za su iya yin nasara a wasan da aka buga da kuma na kusurwa.
Kuma a wannan hanyar ne aka ci wannan ƙwallon.
'Yan Rangers sun kasa hana wani dan wasa wasa wasa, sai Livingston ya bude, sai Declan Gallagher da Robinson suka hada hannu suka tura kwallon zuwa hannun Menga, wanda ya ci kwallo a raga daga tsakiyar yankin.
A wannan lokacin, Rangers sun yi nasara a ragamarsu amma suka sami 'yan wasa a tsakiya kuma mai tsaron gida Liam Kelly bai fuskanci kalubale ba.
Wannan wasan ya ci gaba a cikin rabi na biyu, ko da yake Alfredo Morelos ya yi nasara a kan Kelly.
Scott Pittman ya yi ta buga ƙwallon a ƙafar Alan McGregor na Rangers, kuma Lithgow ya buga kwallo a ƙwallo a wani bugun ƙwallo na Livingston.
An yi ta wucewa a tsaye a yankin Livingston kuma ana ta kai musu hari, yayin da aka nemi hukuncin kisa guda biyu - bayan da aka nemi ƙarar daga Hullgate akan dan wasan sa na baya Glen Middleton da kuma daya don hannu - wanda aka ƙi.
