An kama wasu matasa uku da kuma wani matashi dan shekara 20 da laifin yunkurin kisan kai bayan da aka gano wani matashi dan shekara 16 da ke da raunuka da suka shafi shank a Somerset.
An gano yaron da aka ji masa rauni a yankin Excelsior Terrace na garin Midsomer Norton da misalin karfe 4 na safiyar ranar Asabar.
