"Zabe wa Alkalin kotun Kavanaugh ya nuna kin amincewa da irin wannan rashin tausayi da kuma takunkumin da jam'iyyar Democrat ke yi", in ji Trump a wani taro a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya "ji haushin da kuma fushin" jam'iyyar Democrat a lokacin da aka yi zabensa.
