Zababben shugaban kasar Mexico ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai yi amfani da sojoji ba a kan fararen hula
Zababben shugaban kasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obregador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba amfani da karfin soja a kan fararen hula ba, yayin da kasar ke gab da cika shekaru 50 da samun 'yan makaranta da aka yi kisan gilla.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin a ranar Asabar a Tlatelolco Plaza cewa "ba zai taba amfani da sojoji don zaluntar mutanen Mexico ba".
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojoji sun yi ta harbi a wani dandalin zanga-zanga, suka kashe mutane 300, a daidai lokacin da 'yan daliban hagu ke samun karbuwa a Latin Amurka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin tallafawa matasa 'yan Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kuɗi na wata-wata ga waɗanda ke karatu da kuma buɗe ƙarin jami'o'in jama'a kyauta.
