Amurka ta kara yawan kudaden da take bayarwa don bunkasa fasahar kere-kere
Yayin da China ke kara yin aiki a fannin kere-kere, Amurka za ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa kan bincike a fannin, in ji mai saka jari kuma kwararren masanin kere-kere Kai-Fui Liu, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan bayanin ya zo ne a cikin sanarwar da wasu bangarorin gwamnatin Amurka suka yi game da AI, saboda Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar AI a hukumance.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta bayyana aniyarta na zama mai kirkirar kere-kere a duniya a fannin kere-kere har zuwa 2030.
"Rubanya kasafin kudin da ake kashewa wajen binciken ilimin kere kere zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, ganin cewa duk sauran kasashe suna bin Amurka baya sosai, kuma muna neman yin babban ci gaba a fannin kere kere", in ji Lee.
Ruwa da kasafin kudin zai iya ninka damar samun babban ci gaban da zai faru a Amurka a fannin ilimin kere kere, in ji Lee a wata hira da aka yi da shi a CNBC a wannan makon.
Li, wanda littafinsa mai suna "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa a wannan watan, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a cikin Face++, ɗaya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin ƙirar ƙirar ƙira a China.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin ilimin kere-kere wanda ya ci mafi kyawun dan wasan Amurka, Othello, sannan daga baya ya zama babban jami'in gudanarwa na Microsoft Research kuma shugaban reshen Google a China.
Lee ya fahimci muhimmancin gasar da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi a baya, kamar su DARPA Robotics Challenge, kuma ya yi tambaya lokacin da za a gudanar da na gaba don gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
Masu bincike a Amurka sukan yi aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati, in ji Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ce take daukar mafi kyawun malaman jami'a ba, kamfanoni ne suke karbarsu", in ji shi.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun ɗauki jami'o'i da jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan ilimin artificial a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Li ya yi jayayya cewa sauye-sauye a cikin manufofin shige da fice na iya taimaka wa Amurka don tallafawa ƙoƙarinta a fannin ilimin kere kere.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba wa masu digiri na biyu a fannin ilimin kere kere katin Green Card kai tsaye", in ji shi.
Majalisar zartarwa ta kasar Sin ta amince da shirin bunkasa fasahar kere-kere ta zamani a watan Yulin 2017.
