A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaron Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Hoto ta Hoto, wadda za ta hada kan abokan hulda daga masana'antu da masana kimiyya, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zabe na Hoto na Hoto.
A wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da cewa za ta zuba dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri da ake kira AI Next.
A yau, Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta Amirka tana zuba jari fiye da dala miliyan 100 a kowace shekara a bincike a fannin ilimin kere kere.
