Taron Trump a Yammacin Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara jerin tarukan da za su fara a garin Wheeling, a jihar West Virginia.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na farko cikin jerin tarurrukan da aka shirya wa Trump da mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da rangadin da aka shirya a yankunan da ke kusa da shi, kamar su Tennessee da Mississippi.
A cikin zaben tabbatar da za a zabi shi a matsayin babban alkalin kotun, Trump na neman karfafa goyon bayan jama'a a zaben da ke gabatowa, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar rasa ikon da suke da shi a majalisar dokoki a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana a yau kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yamma ET a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta yanar gizo a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye a YouTube.
Trump zai iya yin magana a kan shari'ar da ake yi a wannan makon kan wanda ya cancanci ya zama babban mai shari'a, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya faru ne a cikin wani yanayi mai cike da tashin hankali saboda zargin da ake yi na aikata laifukan jima'i, tare da wani kuri'ar tabbatar da Majalisar Dattawa da aka dakatar da shi har tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke ci gaba da bincike.
Amma, babban manufar wannan taron shi ne, a taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar sakamakon da ba daidai ba a zaben na watan Nuwamba, domin su sami wani ci gaba.
A cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, ma'aikatan yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun ce wannan taro na mako mai zuwa na da nufin "tabbatar da 'yan sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjayen da suke da shi a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma Majalisar Wakilai".
"Gudanar da majalisa na da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban, har shugaban na tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda ya yiwu, yayin da muke shiga cikin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump, wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
Taron da aka shirya yi a yau da dare a Wesbanco Arena na Wheeling zai iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin 'yan jarida na Pittsburgh", in ji jaridar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, zai zama karo na biyu a cikin wannan wata da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ta yi nasara da kashi 40 a zaben 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican a West Virginia, wanda ke kasa a kididdigar zabe.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya yi kokarin ba shi kwarin gwiwa a zaben", in ji Simon Hender, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
