Woods, wanda ya yi tsalle a wasannin biyu na ranar Asabar, ya nuna fashewar hasken wuta, amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasannin 29 a cikin wasan kwallon kafa da kuma wasan wasan kwallon kafa da kuma wasanni bakwai.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta don wasan hudu na safe, ya koma abokin wasansa Henrik Stenson don wasan hudu da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Kepacka suka ci 2 da 1, suka zama na farko da na uku a duniya.
Ba dukan Turai ba ce ta yi nasara, duk da wannan rana mai sanyi da kuma farin ciki a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
A ranar Asabar, Jordan Spithey da Justin Thomas, 'yan wasan da suka yi nasara sau uku a gasar, sun ci kwallo biyu a ragar Amurka.
