Almanac: Wanda Ya Ƙirƙiri Na'urar Aikin Jigari
Shafi daga littafin almanac na ranar Lahadi da safe: 30 ga Satumba, 1882: kamar yau, shekara 136 da suka wuce, kuma a ranar ne aka haifi mai ilimin kimiyyar nan gaba Johann Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya ƙirƙiro wata hanyar gano da kuma auna radiation, wannan ya kai ga abin da a yanzu ake kira ma'aunin Geiger.
A matsayin ginshiƙin kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger mai auna ya shiga cikin al'adun gargajiya, kamar a cikin fim ɗin 1950 mai suna Bells of Coronado, wanda ya nuna shahararrun masanan kimiyyar cowboy Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan na'urar auna nauyi ce, da ake amfani da ita wajen gano abubuwa masu aiki da iska kamar uranium.
Sa'ad da ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin yadda radiation yake shafan abubuwa na ƙarfe".
Evans: "Ka yi la'akari da wannan, yana da ban mamaki!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kaɗan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma, ƙirar da ke ɗauke da sunansa ta ci gaba da aikinta.
Sabon maganin ya koya wa garkuwar jiki yadda za ta "ga" ƙwayoyin cuta
Wani sabon maganin ya koya wa tsarin jikin mutum ya "duba" ƙwayoyin cuta kuma ya kashe su
Alurar riga kafi tana koyar da tsarin garkuwar jiki yadda za a gane ƙwayoyin cuta da ke da matsala a lokacin da ake ba da magani
Hanyar ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga mai haƙuri kuma a sarrafa su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje
Suna iya ganin furotin da yake cikin ƙwayoyin kansa dabam dabam kuma su sake sakawa
Wata allurar da ake gwaji da ita tana da amfani ga mutanen da suke da ciwon daji dabam-dabam.
Wata mata da aka yi wa allurar da ke koyar da tsarin garkuwar jiki ya gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ta ga ciwon daji na ƙwanƙwasa ya ɓace na fiye da watanni 18.
Hanyar ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin mai cutar, a gyara su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don "duba" furotin da ke cikin cututtukan daji da yawa, wanda ake kira HER2, sannan a sake saka ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzowski, na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Cancer ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakon ya nuna cewa muna da maganin da ke da kyau".
A wani bincike da aka yi, an gano cewa, "a cikin kwayoyin halittar nan, akwai wani abu da ke sa mutum ya yi ciwon daji".
An yi amfani da irin wannan hanyar, wato, cire ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta daga jikin mutum kuma a koya wa ƙwayoyin cuta yadda za su kai hari ga ƙwayoyin cuta na kansa don a magance wani irin cutar ƙanƙara a cikin jini.
Kanye West ya kare Trump ta hanyar saka hat dinsa mai dauke da rubutun MAGA bayan ya fito a SNL.
Ba shi da kyau sosai.
An yi wa Kanye West daura da shi a wani shirin talabijin na Saturday Night Live bayan da ya yi wata hira da aka yi da shi a baya inda ya yaba wa shugaban Amurka Donald Trump kuma ya ce zai tsaya takarar shugaban kasa a 2020.
Bayan ya gabatar da waƙarsa ta uku a wannan karon, mai suna Ghost Town, wanda ya sa hat na baseball tare da taken Make America Great Again, ya yi zanga-zangar nuna rashin jin daɗin jam'iyyar Democrat, kuma ya sake nuna goyon bayansa ga Trump.
"A lokuta da dama ina magana da wani farin mutum, sai ya ce, "Yaya kake son Trump?
Idan ina damuwa da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amurka tun da daɗewa", in ji shi.
SNL ta buɗe da wani wasan kwaikwayo wanda Matt Damon ya fito a ciki, inda tauraron Hollywood ya yi wa'azin shaidar da Brett Kavanaugh ya yi a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa game da zargin da aka yi wa Christine Blazy Ford na cin zarafin mata.
Duk da cewa ba a watsa shi ba, bidiyon da ke nuna West yana cikin hauka ya bazu a shafukan sada zumunta na mai ban dariya Chris Rock.
Ba a sani ba ko Rock ya yi kokarin yi wa West ba'a da wannan rubutu.
West ya kuma yi gunaguni a fili cewa an yi masa ba'a a bayan fage saboda kwalliyarsa.
"Suna yi mini wasan bowling a bayan fage.
Sun ce, "Kada ka fito da wannan hat".
