Binciken fim din Johnny English ya sake yin fim - wani fim mai ban sha'awa na sirri da Rowan Atkinson
A yau, al'ada ce a nemi alamun Brexit a cikin kowane sabon fim na Burtaniya, kuma wannan ya bayyana ya dace da wannan farfadowa ta fim ɗin wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo tare da Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da fim ɗin Johnny English kuma ya dawo a 2011 tare da fim ɗin Johnny English: Dawowar.
Shin wannan ba'a game da yadda muke da banbanci a fili ya zama sabuwar damar fitarwa ta kasa?
Duk da haka, Johnny English mai idanu biyu ya samu damar sake sabunta lasisinsa na yin fim da ya yi wa kasa kasa da kasa dariya, wanda a bisa sunan da ya bayar, ya nuna cewa shi wani irin fim ne da aka tsara don masu sauraron fina-finan da ba Turanci ba.
