Amurka na iya amfani da Sojan Ruwa don "kulle" tare da hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Ministan cikin gida
Washington na iya juyawa zuwa ga sojan ruwanta "idan ya zama dole" don hana Rasha sayar da makamashin a kasuwannin da suka hada da na yankin gabas ta tsakiya, kamar yadda Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, a cewar Washington Examiner.
Zincke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria, inda take aiki a kan gayyatar da ta yi wa halattacciyar gwamnatin, wani abin da ake amfani da shi ne don neman sabbin kasuwanni na makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilan da suka sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne suna son sayar da makamashi, kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin da kudancin Turai", in ji shi, kamar yadda aka ruwaito.
A cewar Ministan, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyi da za a magance ayyukan Rasha.
"Amurka tana da damar, tare da goyon bayan Sojojin Ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa na bude kuma, idan ya cancanta, toshe su, don tabbatar da cewa makamashin Rasha ba zai shiga kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke yana magana ne a taron da kungiyar masu amfani da makamashi ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke da matsayin "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya soki hanyoyin da Washington ke bi wajen tunkarar Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa a zahiri iri daya ne.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha shine, fiye da haka, sake amfani da kuma maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana mai da hankali ga Rasha a matsayin "doki wanda ya san kawai da wata dabara", saboda yana da tattalin arziki wanda ya dogara da mai.
Kalaman na zuwa ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ta dauki nauyin kara yawan isar da iskar gas daga Amurka zuwa Turai, inda zai maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da shi a Turai.
