Wanda ya kirkiro gidan yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kafa sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da za ta yi daidai da ta Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa wani kamfani da yake son ya yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon, da Google.
Sabuwar matattarar wannan babban fasahar ita ce Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke gina kan dandalin Solids na Berners Lee.
Solid Platform yana bawa masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su, da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar da wane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da ya yi da Fast Company, Berners Lee ya yi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce " mamayar duniya".
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", ya ce game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar dandamali na Solid yana bawa masu amfani damar ƙirƙirar "ɗakin ajiyar bayanan lantarki na sirri" ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin lambobi, jerin ayyuka, kalanda, ɗakin kiɗa, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin wannan burauzar a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman game da bayanan sirri na sirri shi ne cewa yana ba wa mai amfani damar yanke shawara game da wanda zai iya samun damar zuwa ga wane irin bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan damar "karfafawa ta hanyar bayanai".
A ra'ayin Inrupt, a cewar kamfanin Shugaba John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya ba da albarkatu, hanyoyin da kuma kwarewar da ta dace don sanya dandalin Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
Kamfanin ya kunshi Berners Lee, Bruce, wani tsarin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu aikin kwangila da suka yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma wata ƙungiyar masu aikin sa kai da suka yi aiki a kan aikin.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya gina aikace-aikacen da ba na jama'a ba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin Inrupt.
Berners Lee ya ce shi da ƙungiyarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za a ba su damar yin canje-canje masu ban mamaki, suna jujjuya tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
"Ba ma tambayar su izini".
A wani rubutu da ya wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "Manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai kare mutuncin ingancin sabon kayan da aka kirkira bisa tsarin Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners Lee ya sauya fasalin Intanet lokacin da ya kafa kungiyar yanar gizo mai suna World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT).
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners Lee ya kasance babbar murya a cikin muhawarar tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Ko da tare da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban kungiyar World Wide Web Consortium, da Web Foundation da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da zamanin Intanet mai zuwa", in ji Berners Lee.
