"A wannan lokacin, za a auna ni da nasara bisa amsar wannan tambayar, 'Zan iya dawo da wannan kungiyar zuwa gasar Premier League?
"Game da tsari da kuma kayan aikin wannan kungiyar, babu shakka tana cikin Premier League", in ji shi.
"Ba abu ne mai sauki ba a samu wannan rukunin a nan, amma zan iya ganin na yi nasara a nan idan na iya dawo da rukunin a nan".
Ross ya fara aikinsa na horarwa ne kawai shekaru uku da suka wuce, bayan da ya yi aiki a matsayin mataimakin koci a Dumbarton da kuma watanni 15 a cikin ma'aikatan horo na Hartz.
Ya taimaka wa Alao daga koma baya daga rugujewa zuwa rukuni na uku kuma ya jagoranci St Mirren daga bakin rugujewa zuwa cin nasarar Gasar Championship a kakar wasa ta gaba.
Ross ya ce ya fi jin dadi a yanzu fiye da yadda ya taba ji a lokacin da yake wasa a Clyde, Hartlepool, Falkirk, St Mirren da Hamilton Academical.
"Ya kasance kamar wani matattarar hanya", in ji shi, yana tuna da zama kocin Auala.
"Na yi tunanin cewa zama kocin ya fi gamsuwa fiye da zama ɗan wasa.
Abin mamaki ne, domin ina yin abin da ya dace, ina samun kuɗi mai yawa kuma na sami ci gaba sosai.
Amma yin wasa yana da wuya.
Dole ne ka jimre wa abubuwa da yawa a mako.
