Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afku a birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar majiyoyin gwamnati, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Tare da katsewar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su sami damar samun bayanai daga Donggala, wani yanki a arewacin Palou, wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai girman Richter 7.5.
A birnin Palu, mutane fiye da 16,000 ne suka ƙaura bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, wanda ke gefen bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a na 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka auku.
Dongala wata masarauta ce da ta kai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 mi) na gabar teku a kudu maso yamma na tsibirin Sulawesi.
Daular, matakin da ke ƙasa da gundumar, yana da kimanin mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan abubuwan da ke tallafawa tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Dongala.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da mahimmanci a cikin lardin, amma ana samun mafi yawa a cikin Morowali, a gefen gabar Sulawesi.
Fadu da Donggala sun sha fuskantar tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya hallaka mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yankin Donggala na yamma a 1996, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin Tsakar Ruwa na Wuta a cikin Pacific Ocean kuma tana fama da girgizar ƙasa.
Wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku kwanan nan su ne:
2004: Wata babbar girgizar kasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ta shafi kasashe 14, inda ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, kuma fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar tekun Sumatra a ƙarshen Mayu da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Neos, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar da ta kai 6.8 a ma'aunin Richter ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, inda ta jawo tsunami da ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane kusan 700 a gabar kudancin ƙasar.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin maki 7.6 a ma'aunin Richter ta afka kusa da birnin Pandang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin maki 7.5 a ma'aunin Richter ta yi wa ɗaya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra rauni, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon kafa 30 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane wajen 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta girgiza yankin Pindi Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba, yayin da ta sa mutane su tuna da bala'in da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004 ya haifar.
Ba a sami tsunami ba a wannan karon, amma an kashe mutane fiye da 100 a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Manyan girgizar ƙasa sun afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda suka kashe sama da mutane 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta rushe dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a cikin matsala na ɗan lokaci.
