Masu gabatar da kara na neman a yankewa wani wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci hukuncin kisa a New York
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman a yanke wa Sayfullo Sayfov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York da ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a saba yi wa wannan jihar ba a kan wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
An zargi Shaipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da motar haya ta kamfanin Home Depot wajen kai hari kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi awon gaba da masu tafiya da masu kekuna da suka tarar da shi a kan titin a ranar 31 ga watan Oktoba.
Don a yanke masa hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su nuna cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "da gangan" kuma ya yi mummunar rauni ga jiki "da gangan", a cewar wata takardar shaidar da aka shigar a kotun da ke Kudancin New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan laifuka sun cancanci hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda takardar ta nuna.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuka 22, da suka haɗa da laifuka takwas na kisan kai a kan ƙungiyar masu aikata laifi, wata dabara da ake yawan amfani da ita a kan shari'o'in aikata laifuka, da kuma laifuka biyu na yin amfani da karfi da kuma lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "tsara da kuma shiri mai zurfi", sun kuma bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin "mai ban tsoro, mai zalunci da kuma rashin hankali".
"Saipfullo Habibullayevich Saipov ya jawo wahala, lalacewa da rashi ga iyalai da kuma abokan Diego Enrique Angellini, Nicholas Cleaves, An-Lor DeKand, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlich, Eran Ferrucci, Eran Diego Mendoza da kuma Alejandro Damian Panukov", in ji sanarwar da aka fitar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun wuce tun lokacin da Kotun Kudancin New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa a kan wani wanda ya cancanci kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake zargi, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa a kan kashe dillalan kwayoyi biyu, amma a karshe aka yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A karshe da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a kan wani lamari na tarayya a New York a shekarar 1953 ne ga ma'auratan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, wadanda aka kashe bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa kan aikata leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin yakin sanyi shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe su a cikin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
