A cewar FWC, ana samun yanayin tabo na rashin daidaituwa a yankunan da ke cikin lardunan Pinellas, Manati, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Wani yanki na Red Tide ya kai kusan kilomita 130 na gabar teku daga yankin arewacin Pinellas zuwa lardin Lee na kudu.
Ana samun kuraje a nisan mil 10 daga gabar ruwan lardin Hillsboro, amma an samu raguwar a wasu wurare fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga ruwan Red Tide a lardin Pasco.
An samu matsakaicin taro a bakin teku da kuma gabar teku a gundumar Pinellas a makon da ya gabata, an samu karamin zuwa babba a bakin teku a gundumar Hillsboro, an samu karamin zuwa babba a gundumar Manati, an samu karamin zuwa babba a bakin teku ko gabar teku a gundumar Sarasota, an samu karamin zuwa matsakaici a gundumar Charlotte, an samu karamin zuwa babba a bakin teku ko gabar teku a gundumar Lee, an kuma samu karamin a gundumar Coalition.
Ana ci gaba da samun cututtukan numfashi a yankunan Pinellas, Manati, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Babu wani rahoto da aka samu na cutar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
